This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) because it deals with natural language processing and image captioning. It could also belong to cs.CV (Computer Vision) because it involves image analysis and captioning. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) because it involves the use of knowledge graphs to augment image captioning. It could also be classified under cs.LG (Machine Learning) because it involves the use of state-of-the-art methods for image captioning. Finally, it could be categorized under cs.IR (Information Retrieval) because it involves the retrieval of information from knowledge graphs to improve image captioning.
